---
title: Savoury Parmesan & Bacon Pancakes with Fennel Salad | Serves 2
description: Craving pancakes but still want that savoury hit? We've got you covered with these cheesy bacon and chive pancakes drizzled
with herby mayo. Serve up with a side salad of fennel and rocket. We think there is no better way to start the day!

*Keep an eye out... Due to sourcing challenges over the Christmas period, some of the fresh ingredients you receive may be slightly different to what’s pictured. Don’t worry, your recipe will be just as delicious!*
